    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’re like a glove, an empty man,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So meaningless without a hand;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, saturate each inward part"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And form Yourself in all our heart."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The Lord must spread into our mind,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our natural thoughts and concepts bind;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Imaginations, dreams be gone,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The kingdom-seed in us is sown!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In our emotions He must grow;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Raw, fragile feelings overthrow;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our love, our hatred, must be His—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, we agree with You for this."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Another part the Lord must fill—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our hard, unbending, stubborn will;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, our resistance quickly break,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Subdue us for Thy kingdom’s sake."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our conscience too the Lord must clear,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That we may walk in godly fear;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our conscience must be keen today,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Else we cannot the Lord obey."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "’Tis by His growing, spreading thus,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The Lord will have His home in us;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "A place on earth where He is Lord,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
